name: Mad Car Parking Simulator - Dimly Parking Lots
name_original: Mad Car Parking Simulator - Dimly Parking Lots
description:
This is an amazing car parking simulator game that requires highest precision!

It sounds esay?No! It's a challenge for everyone,because you need to park cars in the dimly parking lots!

Show your parking car skill and park your cars as soon as possible in the yellow space.
You’ll need to concentrate in order to avoid hit the walls or other parked cars!


Practice your car parking skills in this free car driving game.

Much fun!
